  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><a href=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201506/95d8e2d5-b8fa-4b1e-ae38-0b517ae8e003.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201506/95d8e2d5-b8fa-4b1e-ae38-0b517ae8e003.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; width: 600px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 460px; border-left-width: 0px;\" /></a><span>&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tWork Clothes<br />\n\tCertain occupations require workers to wear work clothes while performing the duies. What do the work clothes look like? Why do the people performing the work need to wear work clothes?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They changed into their work clothes... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) astronauts wearin space suits<br />\n\t2) work clothes of different colours separate works into different departments<br />\n\t3) fire fighters wear fire <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/retardant\" target=\"_blank\">retardant</a> clothing<br />\n\t4) law <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/enforcement\" target=\"_blank\">enforcement</a> wears bullet-proof vests<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tBy the time everything was said and done, it was almost midnight. Originally, Sean had no intention to stay overnight at the office since he had no early meeting the following day, but seeing the time was already so late, he thought he might as well save his commuting time back home and put it towards sleeping. He checked that he did have a clean set of work clothes for the next day. Then he headed out to the shower in the gym downstairs. It was always nice to stand under warm water after a long day at work.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/163868647894/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p740317/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p740317\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p744677/\">中国老师PK英国学生终章：成绩飞涨神逆转</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p744601/\">2015年6月四六级成绩查询今日开始！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p734443/\">2015年6月六级成绩查询入口：99宿舍网</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742251/\">2015年6月大学英语四级查分手册</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p744245/\">给语言学习者：你不知道的9个英语冷知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p744471/\">笑Cry！同个妹子被18国设计师PS 中国版高亮</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p743592/\">看美剧一定要懂的10个习惯表达（上）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p744389/\">歪果仁围观台湾麦当劳女神：酷似玩偶娃娃</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p744305/\">【七夕影院】那些暖心的欧美爱情片</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736167/\">2015年6月英语四级成绩查询入口：99宿舍网</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
